{"tid":2406040,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"故事《動森 Clubhouse》","createTime":"2021-02-13T01:22:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-13T01:23:06.000Z","uid":129010,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a920170a4ebb003be210aeb46f85b77446364423","tid":2406040,"uid":129010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T01:22:20.000Z","msg":"故事《動森 Clubhouse》<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H0aPSvm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH0aPSvm.png&h=0c877713&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n綿羊茶茶丸 註冊了一個帳戶在最近人氣旺盛的語音社交媒體app Clubhouse。它有點像可以互動的podcast 或者是 聲音版本的Twitter。暫時這個應用程式以邀請制推出。因為好朋友倉鼠哈姆 的邀請碼，所以茶茶丸急不可待就加入並試聽各個主題的「房間」的內容⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/W5gBM6gVKZk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FW5gBM6gVKZk&d=kdQtjCisvz5VKkzPdH2zQwDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=41cc9e2b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/W5gBM6gVKZk</a><br />\n<br />\n還有祝各位動森玩家 農曆新年快樂～ 新的一年大吉大利！"},{"pid":"99cfe7293874edb193ce3267f2cc9347e4a5914c","tid":2406040,"uid":129010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T01:23:06.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\">影片截圖</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1L4QBXg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1L4QBXg.jpg&h=63a4ab84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GtuhgXg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGtuhgXg.jpg&h=7de62ba7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wh1b5QB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwh1b5QB.jpg&h=89932825&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uLqDLQB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuLqDLQB.jpg&h=4f2c91dd&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}